features: 【Powerful and Versatile Cleaning 】INSE 6-in-1 cordless vacuum cleaner ideal for hard floors, short-pile carpets, stairs, cars, and more, this vacuum cleaner ensures no spot is left unclean. The stick vacuum's high-speed digital motor delivers robust suction power in max mode, making it a lightweight, versatile, and effective cleaning tool. Experience the ease of use of our 6-in-1 rechargeable stick vacuum, and turn cleaning from a task into a delight!

【45mins Long Runtime and Durability】Enjoy up to 45 minutes of continuous, fade-free cleaning with our rechargeable cordless vacuum. Engineered with over-voltage, over-current, overheat, and short circuit protection, it promises a service life five times longer than average. Charge the detachable battery separately or on the main body. The long-lasting runtime and potent suction power make this cordless stick vacuum cleaner perfect for thorough, whole-home cleaning!

【High-Efficiency Filtration System】Our cordless vacuum cleaner employs a 5-layer high-efficiency filtration system using cyclone separation technology, capturing 99.99% of microscopic dust particles as small as 0.1 microns. This lightweight cordless stick vacuum delivers a dust-free, purified environment for your family, effectively picking up pet hair, fine dust, debris, and large particles.

【Lightweight & Multifunctional 】Transform your cleaning routine with our lightweight, battery-operated stick vacuum. Equipped with a retractable tube and versatile attachments, the cordless vacuum cleaner can clean hard-to-reach areas like curtains and ceilings. Convert it into handheld mode for table cleaning or use it to clean your car seats. Battery stick vacuum only weighing 3lb. It's a 6-in-1 multi cleaning powerhouse, ready to meet all your cleaning needs!

【Flexible LED Motorized Brush Head】Navigate through tricky spots with our flexible cordless vacuum cleaner's LED-lit motorized brush head. The 180° swivel sideways and 90° up and down movement make cleaning under furniture and beds a breeze. The ergonomic handle ensures a comfortable grip for an efficient and satisfying cleaning experience.

【Hassle-Free Maintenance and Storage】Manage your living space effortlessly with our pet hair vacuum cleaner. The large dust cup can be emptied with a single button press, eliminating the need for direct contact with dust or debris. The hardfloor stick vacuum is equipped with a wall-mountable storage option and an attachment storage rack, contributing to an organized, clutter-free space. The detachable, washable, and recyclable filter ensures the vacuum's optimal performance.

【Exceptional Customer Support 】We are committed to providing exceptional customer support round the clock. Our rechargeable cordless stick vacuum cleaner comes with a 12-month after-sales service guarantee for 100% satisfaction. Trust INSE for premium quality products and superior customer service. Remember to clean the filter/sponge regularly to maintain the vacuum's powerful suction.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Something was supposedly $400 plus on sale for this price Has to be the cheapest thing I have ever received. This should’ve been $100 in the beginning on sale for something cheaper. If you want a nice kiss toy or a toy for your kids to use why they’re helping you clean this is the perfect one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is not a carpet cleaner, a shop vac, or a wet vac. Don't buy this for one of those projects.What it is: an efficient, maneuverable, mid-range vacuum for quick jobs and maintenance. It has better suction than a car vac, but it doesn't try to seize every loose item in the room. It's excellent with pet hair (dust kitties), tracking on shoes, settled dust, furniture. It's lightweight, agile, versatile, the perfect detailing tool. Easy to use, easy to empty.Coarse hair in sufficient quantity can clog the tubing and the roller, but it's not difficult to clear.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble and use
reviews.reviewText: I liked the lightweight and the lights on the unit to see the floors. Easy to use an easy to clean. I’m very happy with the unit. Hopefully it has a good lifespan.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Not comparable to expensive brands
reviews.reviewText: Not even close to the auction power of a Shark or Dyson. Also the amazing sales Amazon advertises for Black Friday, Cyber Monday, and Christmas are flat out lies. You can get this vacuum for $100 all the time on the companies website. Lots of paid reviews saying it’s as good as Dyson, etc and it’s flat out not true.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Doesn’t work on carpet with dog fur
reviews.reviewText: It worked pretty good on hard surface but just pushed the fur around on the carpet at its highest level

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a complete junk product. Amazon should be ashamed ! The sweeper head will not detach no matter how hard you pull. The lever clicks because you can hear it but still will not detach. There is no way any average housewife has enough strength to detach the sweeper head to empty the debris. We have had other Inse products which were great but not this model
